channel.title: Unhandled Packet Error
channel.description:
Each time I click someone by the skills tab like Skills tab, Magic tab, and stuff it shows a unhandled Packet, Actually it does it to almost everything I click.
Example of the errors it shows : [IMG]http://i55.tinypic.com/ebbnyq.jpg[/img]
Combat tab error: Unhandled button 120 746 Unhandled Packet [id=216,len=6,data=0x02EA0078FFFF]
Skill tab error: Unhandled button: 121.746 Unhandled packet: [id=216,len=6,data=0x02EA0079FFFF]
Quest tab: Unhandled button: 122.746 Unhandled packet: [id=216,len=6,data=0x02EA007AFFFF]
Diarys tab Unhandled button: 123.746 Unhandled packet: [id=216,len=6,data=0x02EA007BFFFF
Inventry tab Unhandled button: 124.746 Unhandled Packet: [id=216,len=6,data=0x02EA007CFFFF
And so on...
SO PLEASE HELP
Please don't reply if your just gonna say " Learn it yourself " or "Gtfo" or something that wont help me
